---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于 Rex Wang — 老板AI化">
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav>
    <a href="/" class="logo">Rex Wang</a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="/">← 返回首页</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- About Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <div class="profile-photo">
        <img src="/images/profile/rex1024.png" alt="Rex Wang — 王鹏辉" />
      </div>
      <div class="profile-info">
        <span class="section-label">About</span>
        <h1>王鹏辉 <span class="en-name">Rex Wang</span></h1>
        <p class="profile-title">老板AI化 · 高维盈利体系创始人</p>
        <p class="profile-tagline">实战派老师，18年品牌定位授课超1000场</p>
        <div class="profile-tags">
          <span class="tag">18年品牌定位战略顾问</span>
          <span class="tag">AI商业全链路操盘手</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Beliefs -->
  <section class="beliefs-section">
    <span class="section-label">独家核心论断</span>
    <div class="beliefs-grid">
      <div class="belief-card">
        <p class="belief-text">先改变老板，才能改变企业；<br/>老板脱胎换骨，企业才能脱胎换骨</p>
      </div>
      <div class="belief-card">
        <p class="belief-text">老板是发动机，定位是方向盘，<br/>AI是放大器</p>
      </div>
      <div class="belief-card highlight">
        <p class="belief-text">碳基智慧 × 硅基执行力 = <br/><strong>AI核聚变</strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dual Background -->
  <section>
    <span class="section-label">双维实战背景</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">既懂商业本质，又懂AI落地</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">国内少有的"既懂传统企业经营本质，又懂AI智能商业落地"的实战派导师。</p>

    <div class="dual-grid">
      <div class="dual-card">
        <div class="dual-icon">🏢</div>
        <h3>18年实体经营深耕 · 懂商业本质</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>深圳赢想力品牌管理有限公司创始人</li>
          <li>同济EMBA玄奘商途全维增长导师</li>
          <li>连续创业者，深耕品牌定位咨询与企业增长培训18年</li>
          <li>累计服务上千家中小企业</li>
          <li>2015年出版著作《跨界人生》</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="dual-card">
        <div class="dual-icon">🤖</div>
        <h3>AI全链路实战能力 · 懂落地方法</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>AI商业架构师 / AI产品开发者 / 老板AI化导师</li>
          <li>独创"短链商业 × 智能体集群 × AI自进化"创业三元论</li>
          <li>率先提出"中小企业AI转型的核心，是老板AI化"</li>
          <li>一人跑通"顶层架构→AI产品开发→全平台分发→商业变现"完整闭环</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Transformation Proof -->
  <section>
    <span class="section-label">实证标杆</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">自己就是老板AI化的最佳案例</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">不是理论，是亲身实践。</p>

    <div class="transform-card">
      <div class="transform-grid">
        <div class="transform-before">
          <h4>AI化转型前</h4>
          <p>传统品牌咨询公司创始人，核心能力聚焦定位咨询与课程交付，业务边界清晰单一</p>
        </div>
        <div class="transform-arrow">
          <span>核聚变式升级 →</span>
        </div>
        <div class="transform-after">
          <h4>AI化转型后</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>融合18年定位积累 + AI能力，全面打破能力与业务边界</li>
            <li>独立开发行业专属AI模型，打造老板AI化落地工具体系</li>
            <li>全平台持续内容输出，快速建立行业影响力</li>
            <li>跨领域多线推进项目，一人完成过去一个团队的工作量</li>
            <li>公司从单一品牌咨询机构，升级为AI商业科技公司</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Event Gallery -->
  <section>
    <span class="section-label">Events</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">实战现场</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">品牌战略·增长峰会现场</p>

    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <img src="/images/events/huichang01.jpg" alt="品牌战略·增长峰会" class="gallery-img" />
      <img src="/images/events/huichang02.jpg" alt="品牌战略·增长峰会" class="gallery-img" />
      <img src="/images/events/huichang03.jpg" alt="品牌战略·增长峰会" class="gallery-img" />
      <img src="/images/events/huichang04.jpg" alt="品牌战略·增长峰会" class="gallery-img" />
      <img src="/images/events/huichang05.jpg" alt="品牌战略·增长峰会" class="gallery-img" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <span class="section-label">Mission</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">核心使命</h2>
    <div class="mission-card">
      <p class="mission-text">带领10万+企业老板走进AI世界，<br/>用"定位升级 + 老板AI化"跳出同质化内卷，<br/>打造极简组织，实现幸福感创业。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="/">首页</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/rexwangai" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/rexwangai" target="_blank">X / Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://laobanaihua.com" target="_blank">laobanaihua.com</a>
    </div>
    <p class="copyright">© 2026 Rex Wang. Built with AI, for humans.</p>
  </footer>

  <style>
    /* About Hero */
    .about-hero {
      min-height: 60vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
    }

    .about-hero-content {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 900px;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .profile-photo img {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 3px solid var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    }

    .profile-info h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .en-name {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
    }

    .profile-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--accent-light);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .profile-tagline {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .profile-tags {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .tag {
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      background: var(--accent-glow);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--accent-light);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Beliefs */
    .beliefs-section {
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .beliefs-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .belief-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .belief-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .belief-card.highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1));
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .belief-text {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    /* Dual Grid */
    .dual-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .dual-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .dual-icon {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .dual-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .dual-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .dual-card li {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .dual-card li::before {
      content: '▸';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent-light);
    }

    /* Transform */
    .transform-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .transform-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1.5fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .transform-before h4,
    .transform-after h4 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .transform-before p {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .transform-arrow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
    }

    .transform-arrow span {
      background: var(--gradient-1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .transform-after ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .transform-after li {
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 0.4rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .transform-after li::before {
      content: '✓';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent-light);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Gallery */
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .gallery-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .gallery-img:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
    }

    /* Mission */
    .mission-section {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mission-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08));
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 3rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
    }

    .mission-text {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-hero {
        padding: 6rem 1.25rem 3rem;
      }

      .about-hero-content {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .profile-photo img {
        width: 150px;
        height: 150px;
      }

      .profile-info h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }

      .profile-tags {
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .transform-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .transform-arrow {
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
      }

      .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .dual-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
